+/** @file
+  Multiboot2 protocol support for L4TLauncher
+
+  SPDX-FileCopyrightText: Copyright (c) 2025 NVIDIA CORPORATION & AFFILIATES. All rights reserved.
+  SPDX-FileCopyrightText: Copyright (c) 2026 Ahmed Wafdy. All rights reserved. 
